# Input

```jsonc
{
	"items": [
		// biome-ignore format: preserve the nested object formatting
		{"a":1,"b":2}, // keep this trailing comment after the suppressed element
		3,
	],
	"done": true
}

```


# Formatted

```jsonc
{
	"items": [
		// biome-ignore format: preserve the nested object formatting
		{"a":1,"b":2}, // keep this trailing comment after the suppressed element
		3
	],
	"done": true
}

```
